<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-BR">

<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Cloud Engineer Portfolio</title>

  <!-- Google Fonts -->
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

  <!-- Font Awesome -->
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.5.0/css/all.min.css">

  <style>
    :root {
      --bg: #0d1117;
      --card: #161b22;
      --accent: #58a6ff;
      --text: #c9d1d9;
      --title: #ffffff;
    }

    * {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      box-sizing: border-box;
      font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    }

    body {
      background: var(--bg);
      color: var(--text);
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    section {
      padding: 60px 20px;
      max-width: 1100px;
      margin: auto;
    }

    h1,
    h2,
    h3 {
      color: var(--title);
    }

    /* HERO */
    .hero {
      text-align: center;
      padding-top: 100px;
    }

    .hero h1 {
      font-size: 2.5rem;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }

    .hero h2 {
      font-weight: 400;
      color: var(--accent);
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    .buttons a {
      text-decoration: none;
      padding: 10px 20px;
      border: 1px solid var(--accent);
      margin: 5px;
      color: var(--accent);
      border-radius: 6px;
      transition: 0.3s;
    }

    .buttons a:hover {
      background: var(--accent);
      color: #000;
    }

    /* ABOUT */
    .about {
      text-align: center;
      max-width: 700px;
    }

    /* STACK */
    .stack-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(120px, 1fr));
      gap: 20px;
      margin-top: 30px;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .stack-item {
      background: var(--card);
      padding: 20px;
      border-radius: 10px;
      transition: 0.3s;
    }

    .stack-item:hover {
      transform: translateY(-5px);
    }

    .stack-item i {
      font-size: 2rem;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
      color: var(--accent);
    }

    /* PROJECTS */
    .projects {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
      gap: 20px;
    }

    .card {
      background: var(--card);
      padding: 20px;
      border-radius: 10px;
    }

    .badge {
      display: inline-block;
      background: var(--accent);
      color: #000;
      padding: 5px 10px;
      border-radius: 5px;
      font-size: 0.8rem;
      margin-top: 10px;
    }

    /* ARCH */
    .architecture {
      background: var(--card);
      border-left: 4px solid var(--accent);
      padding: 20px;
      border-radius: 8px;
    }

    /* FOOTER */
    footer {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 30px;
      border-top: 1px solid #222;
    }

    footer a {
      color: var(--accent);
      text-decoration: none;
    }

    /* RESPONSIVO */
    @media (max-width: 600px) {
      .hero h1 {
        font-size: 1.8rem;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>

  <!-- HERO -->
  <section class="hero">
    <h1>Seu Nome Aqui</h1>
    <h2>Cloud Solutions Architect in Training</h2>
    <div class="buttons">
      <a href="#"><i class="fab fa-linkedin"></i> LinkedIn</a>
      <a href="#"><i class="fab fa-github"></i> GitHub</a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ABOUT -->
  <section class="about">
    <h2>Sobre Mim</h2>
    <p>
      Em transição para a área de Cloud Computing, estou desenvolvendo habilidades práticas através da Escola da Nuvem.
      Meu foco está em arquiteturas modernas utilizando AWS e IBM Cloud, com forte interesse em automação, serverless e infraestrutura como código.
    </p>
  </section>

  <!-- STACK -->
  <section>
    <h2>Cloud Stack</h2>
    <div class="stack-grid">
      <div class="stack-item"><i class="fab fa-aws"></i>
        <p>AWS S3</p>
      </div>
      <div class="stack-item"><i class="fab fa-aws"></i>
        <p>CloudFront</p>
      </div>
      <div class="stack-item"><i class="fab fa-aws"></i>
        <p>EC2</p>
      </div>
      <div class="stack-item"><i class="fab fa-aws"></i>
        <p>Lambda</p>
      </div>
      <div class="stack-item"><i class="fas fa-brain"></i>
        <p>IBM Watson</p>
      </div>
      <div class="stack-item"><i class="fas fa-code"></i>
        <p>Terraform</p>
      </div>
      <div class="stack-item"><i class="fab fa-docker"></i>
        <p>Docker</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- PROJECTS -->
  <section>
    <h2>Projetos em Destaque</h2>
    <div class="projects">
      <div class="card">
        <h3>Static Website AWS</h3>
        <p>Site hospedado em S3 com distribuição via CloudFront e HTTPS.</p>
        <span class="badge">Live on AWS</span>
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        <h3>Serverless API</h3>
        <p>API construída com AWS Lambda + API Gateway + DynamoDB.</p>
        <span class="badge">Live on AWS</span>
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        <h3>Infraestrutura com Terraform</h3>
        <p>Provisionamento automatizado de recursos cloud usando IaC.</p>
        <span class="badge">Live on AWS</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ARCHITECTURE -->
  <section>
    <h2>Arquitetura do Site</h2>
    <div class="architecture">
      <p>
        Este site é Serverless: Hospedado em S3, distribuído por CloudFront com SSL via ACM e deploy automatizado via GitHub Actions.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- FOOTER -->
  <footer>
    <p>Contato: seuemail@email.com</p>
    <p><a href="#">Chatbot Watson</a></p>
  </footer>

</body>

</html>